        "ScenePath": "assembly:/_pro/scenes/missions/marrakesh/_scene_spider.entity",
        "TileImage": "$($repository 441619df-c52b-4272-b71e-6c289e435c68).Image",
        "Description": "The Davids had two pieces of information that will help us hunt down the mystery client: Orson Mills had a satellite phone with one contact and a password that changes every 40 minutes, and that General Reza Zaydan is the one that changes it. Kill him and most of his officers, leaving the terror cell in the hands of the mostly incompetent Carad Zaydan, Reza&apos;s son that was rapidly promoted due to nepotism. That will allow us to hack the code without interruption, and destroy the terror cell.",
